title: Ep. - 409 - JEN SHAH ARREST REAL HOUSEWIVES OF SALT LAKE CITY REVIEW WITH KEVIN THE DRIVER, SAM THE RECEPTIONIST, AND EMILY D. BAKER
description:
Kate discusses SET on Discovery Plus and Paris in Love on Peacock. SET follows the contestants vying for the “Best of Show” ribbon at the Orange County Fair table setting competition. Paris in Love follows Paris Hilton in the run up to her wedding.

 

Kate discusses the Jen Shah arrest episode on Real Housewives of Salt Lake City with Kevin the driver, Sam the receptionist at Beauty Lab & laser, and Emily D. Baker providing legal insight.
